<title type="text">Adding Geolocation metadata, with microformats, datasets, microdata and RDFa Lite</title>
<link href="http://dev.opera.com/articles/view/geolocation-html-api" />
<author>
<name>karlcow</name>
</author>
<content>In September 2011, I needed to mark up location data in an HTML document and it became more complicated than I initially thought it would be. I started to think about this topic again recently and explored some possibilities. In this article I will share my findings, looking at how I used microformats, datasets, microdata and RDFa Lite to mark up this data, and discussing what the best option might be.</content>
